Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前  有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底兩萬哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭懦弱的人  無法背叛藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作夢之前  我想翱翔天際
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的音樂盒開啟  發出聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點一滴演奏出幸福與勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:01:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前  有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言語是永遠的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  forget  to  try  in  mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛比寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時值西元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴黎萬國博覽會上認識的\N強、娜蒂亞與大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同前往強在勒阿弗爾的家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是企圖奪取"蔚藍之水"\N的邪惡三人組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛著萬能戰車·葛蘭坦\N再度找上門來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強他們搭乘自己製作的飛機\N好不容易逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜引擎故障\N只好迫降在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞的"蔚藍之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟隱藏著什麼樣的秘密呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#03  神秘大海獸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,再這樣下去會沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會像這樣\N盡全力在排水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在明明忙到想跟貓借手來用了\N(意指"忙得團團轉")
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,那個是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方發現遇難者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎停止,右舵15度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-副艦長,準備救助遇難者\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧?只有你們兩個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一隻獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法過來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,你這艘船還真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本跑不快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,這是飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機是指在天上飛的那個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊,坐著就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你們來到亞伯拉罕號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艦長梅比魯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是副艦長,赫蘭少校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您,梅比魯艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧您,我們才能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是軍人的本分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了,那架航空器是你做的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,是我和姑丈一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對航空器也頗有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我們做點調查嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請你們說說\N為什麼會漂到這裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上我已經了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個三人組\N想對你們不利是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然追著這樣的孩子到處跑\N真是群過份的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有人在談論我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一定是在談論人家的美貌\N-一定是在談論我的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"美麗"這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了我而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,是為了我而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快要進入20世紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-還在爭這種沒意義的事情\N-你少多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有時間說這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快去把那架飛機找到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-您說的是\N-您說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨好像停了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,天氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對付海獸\N而出動的美國戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君子不近刑人\N危險遠離,危險遠離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架飛機…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是"蔚藍之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過三天我們會折返法國一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時就讓你們下船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您,梅比魯艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我第一次登上戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以四處參觀嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊,儘管去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-艾爾頓\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你負責照顧這些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的要跟戰艦硬拼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了要得到\N"蔚藍之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦尾左舷有船隻接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些孩子說的鐵製船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長,去找孩子們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們客人到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到艦橋去是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,艦長找你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的船喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾頓先生\N這艘船的全長是多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事是軍事機密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以參觀艦橋喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦是用來殺人的船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到這種東西\N竟然高興成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的客人到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶,是葛蘭迪絲小姐他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還追到海上來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧,副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他們兩三發砲彈打聲招呼\N順便警告他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可當作演習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,主砲發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主砲發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊頭\N我想再離遠點會比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說那是什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是距離再拉開就追不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,性命要緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是貪生怕死\N豈能當得了壞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了"蔚藍之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新型的旋轉砲塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以水壓驅動大砲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不妙\N-不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然開砲太過份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對壞人不需要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過份的船,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑森、韓森,準備應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-收到\N-收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的葛蘭坦竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白旗,快舉白旗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說那什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性命要緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就該這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用吊臂把他們吊起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到法國就交給警方查辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真可憐\N-真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經吃完了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度真快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,因為肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會轉告伙房的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪了,這不是你做的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看不太出來\N但我可是位學者喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學者?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是身負\N美利堅合眾國總統的秘密任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此搭上這艘軍艦的\N海洋學家,艾爾頓博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這艘船上地位僅次於艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才沒有穿軍服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了,強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的生物都能分為兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的,跟難吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於這條魚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於好吃的那一類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幾乎都沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?不吃?\N如此美味的食物?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞,那真是太不幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生就是吃、睡、玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這三項
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而妳竟然白白捨棄其中一項
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想殺害動物\N來成就自己的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳是素食主義者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不曉得嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指不吃肉和魚的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是大王在吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王你吃沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了,你們想不想知道\N這艘船的秘密任務是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說出來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你們答應不說出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就只告訴你們兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我答應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這艘戰艦正在追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界各海域出沒的大海獸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,那我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴黎的報紙看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,這種事\N為什麼要當成機密?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獸又不會看報紙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之,那是軍事機密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,有這麼大艘戰艦的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣的海獸\N都不是對手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是主桅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦首右舷發現疑似海獸物體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝方位104前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-全艦進行海戰戰鬥準備\N-了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員就戰鬥位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一次\N全員就戰鬥位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員就戰鬥位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟航才4天就碰上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們實在走運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟所有砲門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標為右舷大型生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-砲擊準備\N-砲擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,別開火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是海獸也是生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以殺牠\N太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不曉得害死多少船員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測距完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有主砲開始追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位瞄準儀至射擊指揮儀\N傳導正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各砲連動追針開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標距離1萬2千\N速度30節
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30節?這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以相信牠竟然比本艦還快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有主砲完成發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,被牠給逃了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪,好像有東西在追牠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠沒事了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了,給我出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪妳多嘴說那些\N我們才會被趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就不該殺生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不可原諒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N你滿腦子就只有早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明白大王在說什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,其他動物多少也懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻不懂那隻海獸的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是隻邪惡的海獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼可能會懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獸從古代就住在海中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是後來出現的人類\N想要獵殺海獸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,你們在吵什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獸怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我人在廚房,剛好錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在廚房做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做要給海獸的餌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香腸是海獸的餌嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,這也是軍事機密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵牠香腸?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠又不是大王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡無論什麼都是軍事機密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是軍艦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看,這樣海獸就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數萬年前殘存下來的海獸\N可不會只有一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有一公一母當夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就生不出小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來牠們是夫妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是海洋學家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛進海裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獸是爬蟲類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了換氣還會浮出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那邊過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獸從右舷後方接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度32節
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主砲測距還沒好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,目標太過靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副砲呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真走運!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二管區進水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注水至第三火藥庫,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復原傾斜\N啟動右舷排水幫浦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘軍艦裝甲全由鋼鐵打造
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用鋼鐵做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能在船底開洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真的是生物嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獸於左舷徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷齊發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要宰了牠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈開了?是金屬的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一頭海獸呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠在追逐那隻海獸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船會沉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘可是美國海軍的\N最新戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集近代科學精華所建造出的\N亞伯拉罕號是不會沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獸死了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠還活著,又潛下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會被殺死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獸朝艦首右舷筆直前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舵,左滿舵!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左滿舵!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太驚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭主砲直接命中\N竟然還能活命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷前方有物體靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魚雷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,舵轉不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷傾斜7度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主砲轉盤無法轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三、第五管區進水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一砲塔無法旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太不像話了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力進行左舷排水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,我找不到大王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王不見了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,而且戰艦也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒有注意到我們落海了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是艾爾頓…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,妳看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舵被擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法折返了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子就只有大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,如果那真是魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻海獸的真面目\N究竟會是什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待續)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:24:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼應付心中的焦急才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要看不清遠方的夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喃喃自語  仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.27,0:24:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你的約定耀眼閃爍著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.22,0:24:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try  安慰的話語\N是傳達不到內心的風
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然背負的不安逐漸膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.07,0:24:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我自己的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人應該也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.01,0:24:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跌倒或感到迷惘\N仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.06,0:25:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人與一隻動物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸進神秘大海獸的嘴巴裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.50,0:25:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海獸的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.80,0:25:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是世界上首艘實用潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.07,0:25:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強,這艘船一定是海盜船
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.74,0:25:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.88,0:25:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發明出這麼棒東西的人\N不可能會是壞人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.98,0:25:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底兩萬哩  下一回\N「萬能潛水艇鸚鵡螺號」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.82,0:25:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要看喔\N-要看喔
